timestamp.title: Time of each data element, left-labeled (the beginning of time window).

equity.title: Equity value of the account in dollar amount as of the end of each time window.

profit_loss.title: Profit/loss in dollar from the base value.

profit_loss_pct.title: Profit/loss in percentage from the base value.

base_value.title: Basis in dollar of the profit loss calculation.

timeframe.title: Time window size of each data element.
